#Privacy Policy

Drive Talk Mm is an Open Source application published under the MIT license. The project is hosted at [https://github.com/BotTutorials/drivetalkmm](https://github.com/BotTutorials/drivetalkmm), where you can find both the source code and this privacy policy.

We prioritize the protection of your privacy and want to assure you that we do not share or track any user data.

While our application requires permission to access and modify your Google Drive for its functionality, please note that no personal information or data is collected by our program. The only metrics collected are related to the usage of the Google Drive API, which include the number of API requests and the number of errors per second. These metrics are gathered by the Google Drive API itself and are presented to the author of our software in an anonymous manner, without any identifiable information such as account names or IP addresses.

If you have any concerns or questions regarding this privacy policy, please feel free to contact the author via email at khainezay54@gmail.com.
